data.description: Don't miss this rare opportunity! Over 7 acres zoned Ag with a 5 stall barn, tack room and loafing shed. There is a lighted arena, fenced pastures and amazing views! The barn has electric, water and hay storage. This cozy ranch home offers a large eat in kitchen, spacious living room and finished lower level. There is a rec room with a wet bar area, an office, a full bathroom and a bedroom with egress window. If this is your dream, don't wait!
